      "message": "test: extend -unixmaxconnections coverage to assert FD reservation logging\n\nAdd -unixmaxconnections startup checks and assert the new IPC FD\nreservation log line fires with correct values. With -ipcbind=unix\nand -unixmaxconnections=8, the node logs \"Reserving 10 file\ndescriptors for IPC (2 listening sockets, 8 accepted connections)\",\ndemonstrating that this PR increases the reserved FD count.",
