      "body": "> that would require changes to mp::ListenConnections in libmultiprocess\r\n\r\nGood question. libmultiprocess should probably give us a hook to (optionally) control the maximum number of connections. It might be good to draft a PR for that on [bitcoin-core/libmultiprocess](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/libmultiprocess/), or at least open an issue.\r\n\r\nIt doesn't have to a pre-requisite for this PR, it could indeed be a followup.",
